name: InnitForTheTECH
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
INNIT is an ERC 20 token, supporting the development of the INNIT Platform - social analytics & AI-based smart crypto investment tool.

1. Alpha as a Service: Powered by
Social Intelligence - Twitter & Telegram Integration/Data Analysis;
Onchain Analytics - Safety checks & identify smart money movements.

2. Influencer Analytics: identify legit market makers, and their impact on the market, and spot the network of people working together.

3. Campaign management tool: enabling projects to implement fair & transparent Shill-2-Earn campaigns & monitor their community engagement.
